WEBVTT

00:03.065 --> 00:04.331
How you doing?

00:04.333 --> 00:06.300
I'm hungry.
We got any cereal?

00:06.302 --> 00:07.635
Yeah, Cheerios.

00:07.637 --> 00:09.036
I'll have that.

00:09.038 --> 00:10.871
Bowls are in the cabinet.
Help yourself.

00:10.873 --> 00:12.406
Mom used to
get it for me.

00:12.408 --> 00:13.674
Okay.

00:13.676 --> 00:15.910
Well, I'm not your mom.

00:15.912 --> 00:16.944
No kidding.

00:16.946 --> 00:18.479
What are you
getting at, kid?

00:18.481 --> 00:19.714
What's bothering you?

00:19.716 --> 00:22.383
Mom didn't have to get me
cereal, but she did.

00:22.385 --> 00:24.752
She didn't have to put little
notes in my lunch, but she did.

00:24.754 --> 00:28.556
She didn't have to plan family
trips for us, but she did.

00:28.558 --> 00:30.891
Meanwhile, I've asked you,
like, five times,

00:30.893 --> 00:33.360
if we can get a basketball hoop
for this house,

00:33.362 --> 00:34.862
we still don't have one.

00:36.000 --> 00:42.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:43.972 --> 00:47.575
I'm not leaving until
I speak to Theresa Hill.

00:47.577 --> 00:49.777
And I already explained to you,
you can't see her.

00:49.779 --> 00:52.079
I won't leave until
I see Theresa Hill.

00:52.081 --> 00:53.581
Lady, you can demand
all you want.

00:53.583 --> 00:55.516
You're not seeing her.
Step aside.

00:55.518 --> 00:57.685
I won't step aside.

00:57.687 --> 00:58.753
You're holding up the line.

00:58.755 --> 01:00.020
Next.
No. No, no, no, no.

01:00.022 --> 01:01.489
I am not moving!

01:01.491 --> 01:02.757
Out of the way, bitch!

01:02.759 --> 01:04.425
- No!
- Really?

01:04.427 --> 01:06.160
- Settle down.
- No.

01:06.162 --> 01:07.528
No. Get your hands off of me!

01:07.530 --> 01:08.696
Hey, settle down!

01:08.698 --> 01:09.964
That's it.
You're under arrest.

01:09.966 --> 01:11.999
What-- No--
Let me go!

01:12.001 --> 01:13.701
Get your hands off of me!
(handcuffs clicking)

01:13.703 --> 01:16.270
I am here to see Theresa Hill!

01:16.272 --> 01:17.238
Get her out of here.

01:17.240 --> 01:18.539
Take her out.

01:19.541 --> 01:20.741
Next.

01:20.743 --> 01:23.077
My point is, don't let
yourself feel guilty

01:23.079 --> 01:24.478
because Linda's
not around anymore.

01:24.480 --> 01:25.913
Little too late
for that.

01:25.915 --> 01:27.114
Excuse me.

01:27.116 --> 01:29.183
Detectives Reagan and Baez.
You got an assault?

01:29.185 --> 01:30.651
Faith Madson.

01:30.653 --> 01:31.919
Contusions and a laceration.

01:31.921 --> 01:33.654
Said her jerk ex-boyfriend
beat her up.

01:33.656 --> 01:35.990
She's in 12A.
(woman screaming)

01:35.992 --> 01:38.325
MAN:
Hey, that guy's hurting her!

01:39.261 --> 01:40.961
Police! Hey!
MAN: Call security right now!

01:40.963 --> 01:42.530
Get your hands off her.

01:46.067 --> 01:47.468
BAEZ: This the same guy
that assaulted you earlier?

01:47.470 --> 01:49.336
Oh, yeah, yeah.
Raymond Stevens.

01:49.338 --> 01:50.771
(grunts)
Ow!

01:50.773 --> 01:51.839
Help me out here!

01:51.841 --> 01:53.174
Cuff him.

01:53.176 --> 01:54.775
Bitch!
Shut up.

01:54.777 --> 01:56.143
STEVENS: Ow!
DANNY: Yeah, the only bitch

01:56.145 --> 01:58.245
is gonna be you,
when you're locked up

01:58.247 --> 02:00.981
for assault
and strangulation, punk.

02:00.983 --> 02:03.284
Get him out of here.

02:05.020 --> 02:07.121
Hey, you got a woman
in distress?

02:07.123 --> 02:08.255
Yes.

02:08.257 --> 02:10.056
She's right in here.
I called 911

02:10.059 --> 02:12.560
as soon as it started, but
I don't know what to do.

02:12.562 --> 02:14.895
(woman groaning loudly)

02:14.897 --> 02:16.230
Ma'am?

02:16.232 --> 02:19.033
(groaning continues)

02:20.402 --> 02:22.303
Ma'am, are you okay?

02:22.305 --> 02:24.805
This is Officer Reagan.
I'm Officer Janko. (speaking Spanish)

02:24.807 --> 02:26.841
(yelling)

02:26.843 --> 02:28.475
JANKO:
Central, 12 David.

02:28.477 --> 02:31.111
We have a woman in labor
at 135 East 90th Street.

02:31.113 --> 02:32.947
We need a bus
really quick,

02:32.949 --> 02:35.015
and I mean put a rush
on that bus.

02:35.017 --> 02:36.817
That was another contraction?
Y-Yes.

02:36.819 --> 02:38.018
Okay, just stay calm.

02:38.020 --> 02:39.620
I've delivered babies before.

02:39.622 --> 02:41.822
You're gonna be fine.
Deep breaths, okay?

02:41.824 --> 02:43.057
(screaming)

02:43.059 --> 02:45.392
Jamie, Jamie, no.

02:45.394 --> 02:46.894
- No.
- You're gonna okay.

02:46.896 --> 02:48.662
All right? We're here to help you.
Uh-huh. Uh-huh.

02:48.664 --> 02:50.331
Deep breaths, okay?
You're gonna be okay.

02:50.333 --> 02:51.532
(screams)

02:52.767 --> 02:54.902
(screaming)

02:56.705 --> 03:00.705
<b><font color="#00FF00">♪ Blue Bloods 8x07 ♪</font></b>
